        <p><strong>EU Representative:</strong> [To be appointed if required]</p>

        <h3>14.2 Brazil - LGPD (Lei Geral de Proteção de Dados)</h3>
        <p>
            We comply with Brazilian data protection requirements. You have the right to access, correct, delete, and port your data.
        </p>

        <h3>14.3 Australia - Privacy Act</h3>
        <p>
            We comply with the Australian Privacy Principles. Australian users have rights to access and correct their personal information.
        </p>

        <hr>

        <!-- Glossary -->
        <h2>15. Glossary</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Ad Impression:</strong> When an advertisement is displayed in the App</li>
            <li><strong>Device ID / Advertising ID:</strong> Unique identifier for your device used for ads</li>
            <li><strong>GDPR:</strong> General Data Protection Regulation (EU)</li>
            <li><strong>CCPA/CPRA:</strong> California Consumer Privacy Act</li>
            <li><strong>LGPD:</strong> Brazilian data protection law</li>
            <li><strong>Personal Data:</strong> Information that can identify an individual</li>
            <li><strong>Processing:</strong> Any operation performed on data (collection, use, storage, deletion)</li>
        </ul>

